  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Froggle Bunwich</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Froggle Bunwich</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\">Meat</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">item</a> cooked in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> by combining 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Legs\" title=\"Frog Legs\">Frog Legs</a> and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetable\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vegetable\">Vegetable</a>. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\n</p><p>Adding 2 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meat\" title=\"Monster Meat\">Monster Meats</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Lasagna\" title=\"Monster Lasagna\">Monster Lasagna</a>, while adding a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\">Mandrake</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake_Soup\" title=\"Mandrake Soup\">Mandrake Soup</a>. Adding exactly 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twig</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kabobs\" title=\"Kabobs\">Kabobs</a>, but adding 2 will result in Froggle Bunwich. Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Eggs</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\">Pierogi</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Nuggets\" title=\"Honey Nuggets\">Honey Nuggets</a> respectively unless an inedible ingredient such as a bone shard or nightmare fuel is added.\n</p><p><br>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Legs\" title=\"Frog Legs\"><img alt=\"Frog Leg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Leg.png?1afed8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Vegetables Crock Pot(No Mandrake).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Vegetables_Crock_Pot%28No_Mandrake%29.png?2138af\" width=\"466\" height=\"130\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\"><img alt=\"Mandrake.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mandrake.png?c94a2f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\"><img alt=\"Eggs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Eggs.png?a3e7ca\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Leg\" title=\"Frog Leg\"><img alt=\"Frog Leg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Leg.png?1afed8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Veggie.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Veggie.png?80149d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Froggle_Bunwich\" title=\"Froggle Bunwich\"><img alt=\"Froggle Bunwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Froggle_Bunwich.png?bc9d3e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Legs\" title=\"Frog Legs\"><img alt=\"Frog Legs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Legs.png?523667\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Cap\" title=\"Red Cap\"><img alt=\"Red Cap.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Red_Cap.png?468bf1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Froggle_Bunwich\" title=\"Froggle Bunwich\"><img alt=\"Froggle Bunwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Froggle_Bunwich.png?bc9d3e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/24px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a> A recipe for Froggle Bunwich that extenuates hunger value.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Legs\" title=\"Frog Legs\"><img alt=\"Frog Legs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Legs.png?523667\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Carrots\" title=\"Carrots\"><img alt=\"Carrots.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Carrots.png?d06e20\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Froggle_Bunwich\" title=\"Froggle Bunwich\"><img alt=\"Froggle Bunwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Froggle_Bunwich.png?bc9d3e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Leg\" title=\"Frog Leg\"><img alt=\"Frog Leg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Leg.png?1afed8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lichen\" title=\"Lichen\"><img alt=\"Lichen.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lichen.png?e5cd66\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moleworm\" title=\"Moleworm\"><img alt=\"Moleworm.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Moleworm.png?2334f1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Froggle_Bunwich\" title=\"Froggle Bunwich\"><img alt=\"Froggle Bunwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Froggle_Bunwich.png?bc9d3e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/64px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td><td>Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a> requires another inedible ingredient or results in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kabobs\" title=\"Kabobs\">Kabobs</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Leg\" title=\"Frog Leg\"><img alt=\"Frog Leg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Leg.png?1afed8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mushrooms\" title=\"Mushrooms\"><img alt=\"Mushrooms.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mushrooms.png?53