alt=\"Mushrooms.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mushrooms.png?539043\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\"><img alt=\"Eggs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Eggs.png?a3e7ca\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moleworm\" title=\"Moleworm\"><img alt=\"Moleworm.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Moleworm.png?2334f1\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Froggle_Bunwich\" title=\"Froggle Bunwich\"><img alt=\"Froggle Bunwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Froggle_Bunwich.png?bc9d3e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/64px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td><td>Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Eggs</a> requires <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moleworm\" title=\"Moleworm\">Moleworm</a> or results in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\">Pierogi</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/WX-78\" title=\"WX-78\">WX-78</a> will refer to a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog\" title=\"Frog\">Frog</a> as a &quot;potential bunwich&quot;.</li>\n<li>During the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_Fiesta\" title=\"Pig Fiesta\">Pig Fiesta</a> event in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC, Froggle Bunwich takes on a more festive appearance.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Froggle_Bunwich_in_Terraria.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Froggle Bunwich in Terraria\"><img alt=\"Froggle Bunwich in Terraria\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Froggle_Bunwich_in_Terraria.png?2ecdf3\" width=\"120\" height=\"93\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Froggle Bunwich in Terraria</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:CD_frogglebunwich.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\"><img alt=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/CD_frogglebunwich.png/120px-CD_frogglebunwich.png?99d866\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/CD_Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"CD Don&#x27;t Starve\">CD Don&#x27;t Starve</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Froggle_Bunwich_128x128.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\"><img alt=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Froggle_Bunwich_128x128.png/120px-Froggle_Bunwich_128x128.png?95d287\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Froggle_Bunwich#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Froggle_Bunwich#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
