  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nFroggle Bunwich\nNormal\nPig Fiesta\nFood Info\n37.5\n20\n5\nMeat\nObject Info\n15 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nSource\n: ( ×5)\nCooking Info\nx1 x1 x2\n40 sec\n1\nMiscellaneous\n\"frogglebunwich\"\n“A very leggy sandwich.”\n–Wilson\n“Maybe I won't notice that it's frog legs in the sandwich.”\n–Willow\n“Is sandwich with tasty leg meat.”\n–Wolfgang\n“I never thought frog's legs could look so good.”\n–Wendy\n“DELICIOUS FROG FUEL”\n–WX-78\n“Not typically served on a sandwich, but I'll give it a go!”\n–Wickerbottom\n“You can really taste the swamp.”\n–Woodie\n“Has a bit of a kick to it.”\n–Maxwell\n“Ah. Some sustenance I can digest.”\n–Wagstaff\n“What a treat!”\n–Wigfrid\n“Sandwich for me, frog legs for him.”\n–Webber\n“Not a bad afternoon snack.”\n–Walani\n“Ah, French cuisine!”\n–Warly\n“Newt sandwich!”\n–Woodlegs\n“A BUN O' FROGGY”\n–Wilba\n“Fills belly”\n–Wormwood\n“Swamp on a bun.”\n–Wheeler\n“It's really not as bad as it looks.”\n–Winona\n“Mortals are weird.”\n–Wortox\n“This a bad sandwich.”\n–Wurt\n“You can make anything into a sandwich if you try hard enough.”\n–Walter\n“I've been told it's a local delicacy.”\n–Wanda\nFroggle Bunwich is a Meat Food item cooked in the Crock Pot by combining 1 Frog Legs and 1 Vegetable. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\nAdding 2 Monster Meats will result in Monster Lasagna, while adding a Mandrake will result in Mandrake Soup. Adding exactly 1 Twig will result in Kabobs, but adding 2 will result in Froggle Bunwich. Adding Eggs or Honey will result in Pierogi or Honey Nuggets respectively unless an inedible ingredient such as a bone shard or nightmare fuel is added.\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires:\nRequires:\nExcludes:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\n×2\nExamples[edit | edit source]\n×2\nA recipe for Froggle Bunwich that extenuates hunger value.\n×2\nAdding Twigs requires another inedible ingredient or results in Kabobs\nAdding Honey requires Moleworm or results in Honey Nuggets\nAdding Eggs requires Moleworm or results in Pierogi\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nWX-78 will refer to a Frog as a \"potential bunwich\".\nDuring the Pig Fiesta event in the Hamlet DLC, Froggle Bunwich takes on a more festive appearance.\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nFroggle Bunwich in Terraria\nOriginal HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don't Starve.\nIcon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
