  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Bunwich Froggle là một Món Thịt được nấu trong Nồi Hầm bằng cách kết hợp 1 Đùi Ếch và 1 Rau. Phải mất 40 giây để nấu ăn.</p>",
  "title": "Froggle Bunwich",
  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|foodType = [[Food_Type#Meat|Meat]] [[File:Meats.png|32px|link=Food_Type#Meat]]\n|icon = <gallery>\nFroggle Bunwich.png|Normal\nFroggle Bunwich (Pig Fiesta).png|Pig Fiesta\n</gallery>\n|image = Froggle Bunwich Dropped.png\n|foodRecipe = {{Pic|32px|Frog Leg}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Vegetables}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x2\n|hpRestored     = 20\n|hungerRestored = 37.5\n|sanityRestored = 5\n|cooktime       = 40 sec\n|priority       = 1\n|spoil          = 15 Days\n|stack          = 40\n|canBeBurned=1\n|soldBy ={{Ham}}: {{Pic|32|The Sterling Trough Deli}} ({{Pic|24|Oinc}} &times;5)\n|spawnCode      = \"frogglebunwich\"\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = A very leggy sandwich.\n|willow = Maybe I won't notice that it's frog legs in the sandwich.\n|wolfgang = Is sandwich with tasty leg meat.\n|wendy = I never thought frog's legs could look so good.\n|wx78 = DELICIOUS FROG FUEL\n|wickerbottom = Not typically served on a sandwich, but I'll give it a go!\n|woodie = You can really taste the swamp.\n|maxwell = Has a bit of a kick to it.\n|wagstaff = Ah. Some sustenance I can digest.\n|wigfrid = What a treat!\n|webber = Sandwich for me, frog legs for him.\n|walani = Not a bad afternoon snack.\n|warly = Ah, French cuisine!\n|woodlegs = Newt sandwich!\n|wilba = A BUN O' FROGGY\n|wormwood = Fills belly\n|wheeler = Swamp on a bun.\n|winona = It's really not as bad as it looks.\n|wortox = Mortals are weird.\n|wurt = This a bad sandwich.\n|walter = You can make anything into a sandwich if you try hard enough.\n|wanda = I've been told it's a local delicacy.\n|choose = wolfgang\n}}\n'''Froggle Bunwich''' is a [[Meat]] [[Food]] [[item]] cooked in the [[Crock Pot]] by combining 1 [[Frog Legs]] and 1 [[Vegetable]]. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\n\nAdding 2 [[Monster Meat]]s will result in [[Monster Lasagna]], while adding a [[Mandrake]] will result in [[Mandrake Soup]]. Adding exactly 1 [[Twigs|Twig]] will result in [[Kabobs]], but adding 2 will result in Froggle Bunwich. Adding [[Eggs]] or [[Honey]] will result in [[Pierogi]] or [[Honey Nuggets]] respectively unless an inedible ingredient such as a bone shard or nightmare fuel is added.\n\n__NOTOC__\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires: [[File:Frog Legs ava.png|link=Frog Legs]]\n* Requires: [[File:Vegetables Crock Pot(No Mandrake).png|link=Vegetables]]\n* Excludes: [[File:Mandrake.png|link=Mandrake]] [[File:Eggs.png|link=Eggs]] [[File:Sweetener.png|link=Sweetener]]\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Frog Leg\n|item2 = Vegetables\n|item3 = Filler\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Froggle Bunwich\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Frog Legs\n|item2 = Red Cap\n|item3 = Twigs\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Froggle Bunwich\n|note = {{Pic24|Prototype}} A recipe for Froggle Bunwich that extenuates hunger value.\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Frog Legs\n|item2 = Carrots\n|item3 = Berry\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Froggle Bunwich\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Frog Leg\n|item2 = Lichen\n|item3 = Twigs\n|item4 = Moleworm\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|dlc = Reign of Giants\n|result = Froggle Bunwich\n|note = Adding [[Twigs]] requires another inedible ingredient or results in [[Kabobs]]\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Frog Leg\n|item2 = Mushrooms\n|item3 = Honey\n|item4 = Moleworm\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Froggle Bunwich\n|dlc = Reign of Giants\n|note = Adding [[Honey]] requires [[Moleworm]] or results in [[Honey Nuggets]]\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Frog Leg\n|item2 = Mushrooms\n|item3 = Eggs\n|item4 = Moleworm\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Froggle Bunwich\n|dlc = Reign of Giants\n|note = Adding [[Eggs]] requires [[Moleworm]] or results in [[Pierogi]]\n}}\n\n== {{pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* [[WX-78]] will refer to a [[Frog]] as a \"potential bunwich\".\n* During the [[Pig Fiesta]] event in the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC, Froggle Bunwich takes on a more festive appearance.\n\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nFroggle Bunwich in Terraria.png|Froggle Bunwich in Terraria\nCD frogglebunwich.png|Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from [[CD Don't Starve]].\nFroggle Bunwich 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\n</gallery>\n\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n[[fr: Sandwich de grenouille]]\n[[vi:Bunwich Đùi Ếch]]\n[[ru:Сэндвич из лягушки]]\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Healing]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Meats]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]"
